# Radicale htpasswd credentials for the forty-two-watts calendar sidecar.
#
# This is an EXAMPLE. Before enabling the calendar feature:
#
#   cp radicale/config/users.example radicale/config/users
#   htpasswd -B radicale/config/users fortytwowatts     # set a real password
#
# (Each line is "<username>:<bcrypt-hash>". Don't leave the placeholder below
# in the live "users" file — it is not a valid login.)
#
# Then enter the SAME username + password in the 42W dashboard under
# Settings → Calendar, and subscribe your calendar app to
#   http://<host-ip>:5232/fortytwowatts/energy/
#
fortytwowatts:REPLACE_ME_WITH_htpasswd_-B_OUTPUT
